        "summary":  "CIOs identify AI value realization as their top challenge, with 71% struggling to prioritize impactful use cases and 59% of AI initiatives failing to reach production. Cybersecurity threats have intensified with AI-enabled attacks, while organizations must balance shadow AI containment with enabling employee innovation. Legacy modernization, workforce transformation, and the evolving CIO role complete the landscape of critical pressures facing IT leadership.",
