        "summary":  "An IBM Institute for Business Value study reveals that more than 70% of enterprise leaders find it challenging to switch primary AI providers. The research highlights growing concerns about vendor lock-in as organizations embed AI deeper into operations, with regulatory bodies like the UK Competition and Markets Authority and European Commission increasingly investigating market gatekeeping practices by major cloud providers.",
