        "execSummary":  "The trust gap revealed here ΓÇö 25% trust AI fully, but 80%+ expect it to make material business decisions within 12 months ΓÇö represents one of the most consequential misalignments in enterprise AI deployment today. Organizations are accelerating autonomy faster than they are building the oversight and accountability structures needed to manage it responsibly. For customer support leaders, this is directly applicable: if AI agents will handle escalation decisions, refund approvals, or account actions, the governance framework for those decisions needs to exist now, not after deployment. The workforce redesign signal is also important ΓÇö support roles will shift from doing to supervising AI outputs, requiring proactive reskilling investment.",
