        "execSummary":  "This benchmarking report gives enterprise leaders something concrete: a ranked confidence map of 101 agentic AI tasks, showing where technical practitioners believe agents are reliable today versus where they remain risky. High-confidence zones cluster around structured, bounded tasks ΓÇö report generation, code review, data transformation ΓÇö while lower confidence persists around open-ended reasoning and multi-system coordination. For support and operations leaders building agent roadmaps, this is a practical prioritization tool: start with high-confidence task categories, build governance experience, then expand to harder workflows. The Microsoft sponsorship introduces potential framing bias toward Microsoft\u0027s own agentic offerings (Copilot, Azure AI Foundry).",
